   | READER | REAL | RECEIVED | RECURSIVE | REF | REMOTE | REMOVE | REQUIRED | REVERSE_VIDEO
   | SAVE | SECURE | SHARED | SHAREDBYALL | SHAREDBYRUNUNIT | SHARING | SHORT_DATE | SQL | SYMBOL
